Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.71,0:00:03.80,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ever since the powers of the Soul Reaper\Nwere thrust upon me,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.80,0:00:05.35,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,my whole world has changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.85,0:00:07.69,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I’m Substitute Soul Reaper,\NIchigo Kurosaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.69,0:00:11.77,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I wield this sword\Nwith all of my soul and strength
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.77,0:00:14.56,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,to protect my precious friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.40,0:00:25.36,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You are my one and only.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.36,0:00:30.84,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,No one can take your place.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.09,0:00:36.21,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Never fade, my only flower.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.22,0:00:49.56,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The sun never blinds you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.56,0:00:54.93,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You are like a flower that blooms in shade.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.93,0:01:04.71,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Exhale those feelings you hold inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.71,0:01:14.56,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You are my one and only;\Nnow and forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.56,0:01:24.96,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The day may come\Nwhen all will rise against us,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.22,0:01:30.12,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,but I will protect you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.12,0:01:34.20,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Never give up, my only flower.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.20,0:01:40.79,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,TIME NOTICE THAT\NYOU SHOULD NOTICE THAT
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.93,0:01:44.58,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,NOTICE THAT THERE’S NO OTHER
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.27,0:01:50.69,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What do we do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.16,0:01:53.93,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What--? How--?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.68,0:01:56.37,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,– What…\N– Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.37,0:01:59.82,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Stop repeating yourself!\NIt's annoying.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.82,0:02:00.80,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What did you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.80,0:02:02.91,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I said, “You're annoying!”
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.91,0:02:05.21,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Say something after you've\Nstraightened out your thoughts!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.21,0:02:07.66,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you care what I think?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.66,0:02:09.27,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's none of your business!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.12,0:02:11.64,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Want to fight?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.64,0:02:13.11,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Bring it on!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.40,0:02:15.32,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it, both of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.32,0:02:17.08,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. It's childish!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.71,0:02:26.31,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Inoue… Do you remember anything about\Nwhen you were caught by them?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.37,0:02:30.50,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! I remember a little!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.88,0:02:32.06,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,There was tea!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.17,0:02:34.26,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Tea?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.26,0:02:36.73,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! There were also Japanese sweets!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.06,0:02:39.20,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Inoue, that's enough…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.20,0:02:40.20,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.20,0:02:43.42,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,At any rate, we have to hurry\Nand save Sado!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.42,0:02:46.97,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I can't forgive them for mocking me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.97,0:02:49.18,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,They're mod-souls, just like I am!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.18,0:02:51.71,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,We still can't contact Urahara.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.71,0:02:54.09,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Judging by the way Yoruichi\Nwas rushing…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.09,0:02:55.39,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What in the world's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.39,0:02:57.23,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Are you listening?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.23,0:02:59.18,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'm what you would call\Ntheir elder! But--
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.18,0:03:00.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.52,0:03:02.28,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What confuses me the most is why…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.28,0:03:06.36,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,they have to come and set up\Nthese tedious games.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.90,0:03:11.18,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,There's a lot we don't know!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.85,0:03:19.07,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Soi Fon did?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.36,0:03:20.35,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yes…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.35,0:03:24.12,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It seems she went off somewhere alone\Nright before the passage was cut off.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.12,0:03:27.72,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Without taking the punishment force?\NIs that true?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.72,0:03:30.78,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yes… Omaeda said so…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.19,0:03:33.25,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.52,0:03:36.99,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It’s something that Yoruichi Shihoin\Nand Ukitaki planned
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.99,0:03:39.48,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,and are putting into effect!\NLeave it alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.39,0:03:44.63,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That aside, how did you get\Nthat information from Omaeda?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.28,0:03:49.08,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Weren't you here all day finishing\Nyour paperwork?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.08,0:03:50.46,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yes…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.46,0:03:53.61,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I went out…for a moment…\Nand ran into him…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.61,0:03:55.42,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I see. For a moment, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.42,0:04:00.14,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Then…what's that mountain of documents\Ndoing hiding behind the sofa?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.08,0:04:03.88,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Matsumoto!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.52,0:04:10.42,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, where are you going?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.73,0:04:12.66,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,There's no point in staying here…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.08,0:04:15.39,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go back to Urahara's Shop!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.69,0:04:18.33,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But Chad and our classmates are…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.33,0:04:20.75,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,No…they're probably still all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.36,0:04:25.05,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,They're very loyal to\Nthe game's rules.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.44,0:04:27.61,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,We can assume that no harm\Nwill come to them
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.61,0:04:29.90,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,outside of the challenge.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.99,0:04:36.38,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What's this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.05,0:04:46.02,OS,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Destroy the gate within\Nthirty minutes. By Lirin
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.40,0:04:46.02,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,“Destroy the gate within thirty minutes…”
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.28,0:04:47.06,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Gate?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.06,0:04:48.56,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.61,0:04:55.93,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What's this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.69,0:05:03.75,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's huge…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.02,0:05:07.95,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But nothing can be this big…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.95,0:05:09.71,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's got to be another hallucination.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.44,0:05:12.92,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's opening again!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.86,0:05:16.91,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.66,0:05:22.65,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Kurosaki, what about your body?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.65,0:05:24.66,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'll worry about that later! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.10,0:05:33.83,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,– Hurry!\N– Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.00,0:05:39.82,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.73,0:05:44.64,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.96,0:05:46.58,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's Reishi residue…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.73,0:05:50.23,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,They sure are faster than expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.68,0:05:53.24,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'll send this data to the Soul Society.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.24,0:05:56.46,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,All right. Ukitaki should be ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.16,0:06:02.46,OS,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ninth Communication
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.81,0:06:08.77,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You’re here, just as I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.31,0:06:11.31,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! You came, genius boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.15,0:06:13.13,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Want some?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.13,0:06:14.62,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'll pass!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.01,0:06:16.18,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to interfere.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.61,0:06:17.71,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Hitsugaya.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.12,0:06:20.94,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What are you two old guys\Ndoing together?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.94,0:06:22.57,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,A bit of investigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.06,0:06:26.69,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, Soi Fon is sending data\Nfrom the World of the Living.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.65,0:06:30.66,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Was that why you closed\Nthe Senkaimon?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.66,0:06:34.16,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah… It's easier to collect data\Non foreign elements
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.16,0:06:38.01,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,if we temporarily block\Nthe passage of souls.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.01,0:06:39.00,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Foreign elements?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.00,0:06:42.87,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah… I'm trying to figure out\Nwhat it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.59,0:06:47.21,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be…\Nrelated to the Aizen incident?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.05,0:06:51.11,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know…\NEverything's just beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.46,0:06:52.24,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.28,0:06:55.72,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,She's obtained a Reishi sample!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.21,0:06:57.69,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'll put it in the analyzing machine!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.69,0:06:59.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.44,0:07:02.32,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,There's no corresponding data!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.80,0:07:05.20,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Rin! Analyze it once more!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.20,0:07:06.40,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.40,0:07:07.07,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.07,0:07:09.40,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,– Yeah… It's odd.\N– New data, uploading.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.40,0:07:10.46,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Correction value…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.46,0:07:11.87,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,At any rate, it seems we should…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.87,0:07:14.56,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,– look into this a little more.\N– There really is no data!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.56,0:07:15.57,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Try it once more!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.04,0:07:21.91,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Wha--?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.91,0:07:25.48,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Looking at it close up,\Nit's incredibly huge!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.16,0:07:31.35,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.34,0:07:34.82,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think?\NIsn't this amazing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.20,0:07:37.66,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Just cut it out and tell us\Nyour plan already!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.97,0:07:40.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you doing this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.56,0:07:43.20,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It wouldn't be any fun if I told you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.20,0:07:45.76,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,We're still in our final battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.28,0:07:48.42,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to tell you after everything\Nis settled!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.56,0:07:51.63,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, hold on to something!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.61,0:07:57.97,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,This…is an illusion?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.97,0:08:00.85,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I-I can't breathe…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.85,0:08:01.44,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.75,0:08:02.51,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Kon!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.81,0:08:06.48,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't sew me together\Nvery good! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.06,0:08:09.66,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,We've pretty much won.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.66,0:08:12.11,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Can they do anything?\NThey can't, can they?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.11,0:08:13.46,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Well, of course…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.71,0:08:16.68,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You should just admit defeat!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.92,0:08:19.21,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.21,0:08:20.93,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,We won't give in to the likes of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.24,0:08:22.90,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Then…what's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.78,0:08:25.87,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be…you even got Urahara?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.56,0:08:29.34,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,So what are you going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.96,0:08:35.31,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,– Ishida!\N– Kurosaki…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.81,0:08:37.23,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I-I…can't…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.78,0:08:38.81,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Inoue!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.04,0:08:43.08,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.40,0:08:50.97,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What incredible power!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.97,0:08:53.08,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Renji! Take care of Inoue!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.99,0:08:56.13,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,At this rate, it can't be helped!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.50,0:08:58.10,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You idiot, what are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.01,0:09:09.51,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Stop! If you use your Bankai here,\Nthe whole town will…!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.84,0:09:12.48,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's better than having\Nthe whole town sucked in!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.85,0:09:17.52,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ban…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.71,0:09:21.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Ichigo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.15,0:09:23.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Kurosaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.27,0:09:42.33,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.95,0:09:45.45,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?! Why am I…?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.45,0:09:47.05,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! Inoue!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.05,0:09:48.28,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be that you came\Nto save me--?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.28,0:09:49.31,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ishida!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.31,0:09:50.32,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I guess not…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.76,0:09:54.12,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Where are we?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.12,0:09:57.78,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Who knows…\NI think we're inside the gate.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.77,0:10:00.63,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ishida! Inoue!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.20,0:10:02.30,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.14,0:10:05.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Kurosaki! Renji!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.99,0:10:08.40,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness… You're all okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.40,0:10:09.42,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,All right…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.57,0:10:12.75,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Where in the world are we?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.33,0:10:15.61,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Is this the alternate dimensional space\Nyou were talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.61,0:10:16.54,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Who knows…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.32,0:10:26.28,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's amazing you didn't die.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.61,0:10:29.59,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I won't forgive you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.59,0:10:33.21,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Can you say that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.91,0:10:35.03,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Chad!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.40,0:10:36.22,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Well then…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.22,0:10:39.00,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You've all lived this long,\Nso I'll give you a special surprise!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.36,0:10:41.46,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,A challenge stage!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.63,0:10:45.50,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What's this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.92,0:10:49.15,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Noba and Kurodo will also participate\Nin the challenge stage!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.15,0:10:53.96,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Well…I'm so glad that we get\Nto show you our true powers!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.96,0:10:55.13,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't we, Noba?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.13,0:10:56.48,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm? Yeah…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.77,0:10:59.50,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on! Is that all you can say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.50,0:11:00.97,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You're too relaxed!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.97,0:11:02.95,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That's enough! Shut up, Kurodo…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.95,0:11:05.72,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The time limit is unbelievable!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.72,0:11:06.92,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,A great deal, at five minutes!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.36,0:11:10.89,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! Save Big Brother within that time!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.27,0:11:12.86,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.60,0:11:18.57,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,An hourglass?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.95,0:11:20.87,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,This is the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.16,0:11:26.42,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,All right, let the challenge stage begin!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.55,0:11:33.48,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Let the challenge stage begin!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.22,0:11:37.00,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ishida, take care of Inoue!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.00,0:11:38.24,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.24,0:11:40.49,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Ask me to help, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.25,0:11:43.95,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,How about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.95,0:11:45.28,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ta-dah!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.29,0:11:56.04,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That bastard! He copied Ichigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.04,0:11:57.54,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Which is the real one?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.54,0:11:59.51,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think you're doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.85,0:12:01.71,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That’s my line, you fake!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.08,0:12:07.22,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Roar, Zabimaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.83,0:12:08.78,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You're not getting away!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.79,0:12:14.76,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Wha--?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.06,0:12:22.57,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.57,0:12:26.08,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He can throw out whatever\Nhe sucks in somewhere else?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.08,0:12:27.97,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What crazy power!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.94,0:12:31.44,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.71,0:12:41.61,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, if you don't hurry,\Nyour friend will be buried in sand!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.61,0:12:42.15,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.38,0:12:45.48,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Chad!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.48,0:12:46.42,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.05,0:12:53.07,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Be careful!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.07,0:12:53.69,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.74,0:12:56.70,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,We're close!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.59,0:13:23.68,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.68,0:13:24.56,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.95,0:13:26.00,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Send the data!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.24,0:13:32.10,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,We're receiving video information!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.96,0:13:34.23,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,This is…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.10,0:13:40.97,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Don't stop a man and a woman from\Nhaving a good time together.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.35,0:13:43.70,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You were trying to suck out his soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.32,0:13:45.94,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.72,0:13:49.00,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You'll find out in time!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.08,0:13:53.20,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Shall I chase her?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.20,0:13:53.96,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,No…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.79,0:13:56.57,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,She seems like she's good\Nat running away.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.43,0:13:58.83,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You sent the data, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.83,0:14:01.84,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! Who was she?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.84,0:14:05.50,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah… It's the first time\NI've seen her.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.50,0:14:09.85,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Soi Fon, go back and report the details\Nto Ukitake and the others!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.85,0:14:10.60,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.61,0:14:13.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Sentaro, are you there?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.89,0:14:14.73,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.81,0:14:17.10,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The investigation is finished!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.72,0:14:20.21,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Take down\Nthe passage barrier immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.57,0:14:22.21,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! I understand!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.91,0:14:27.61,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Well, we're finished for tonight.\NGood night.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.61,0:14:30.62,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Hitsugaya…\NCan you help me tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.14,0:14:33.59,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I don't mind…\NWhat do you want me to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.65,0:14:35.35,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.42,0:14:41.43,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's useless!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.85,0:14:43.93,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Then what about this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.87,0:14:54.97,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo! Are you all right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.97,0:14:55.87,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.08,0:15:00.28,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you finished?\NTime's almost up!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.63,0:15:03.72,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Chad!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.12,0:15:06.60,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's absolutely hilarious that
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.60,0:15:09.60,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,you're trying to defeat us\Nwith such slow attacks!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.48,0:15:14.16,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Now for the final attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.16,0:15:18.25,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.52,0:15:21.03,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,– Kurosaki!\N– Again?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.00,0:15:25.85,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Do your Bankai!\NIt's our only choice!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.85,0:15:26.76,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.80,0:15:33.80,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ban…!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.48,0:15:41.74,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.12,0:15:50.37,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,– What?!\N– Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.12,0:15:52.54,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! A light!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.54,0:15:53.27,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.42,0:15:58.28,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Chad!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.54,0:16:06.49,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Chad, are you all right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.49,0:16:07.45,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.45,0:16:08.59,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'll untie you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.59,0:16:09.28,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,No…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.85,0:16:12.48,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It seems it loosened…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.48,0:16:13.52,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.32,0:16:15.93,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Sado!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.48,0:16:19.16,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness you're safe!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.16,0:16:19.92,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.48,0:16:23.54,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Chad… Did something happen\Nwhile you were captured?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.64,0:16:26.80,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,There was tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.80,0:16:28.47,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,See?! I told you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.47,0:16:31.44,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,There really was, wasn't there?! Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.99,0:16:39.04,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.41,0:16:40.41,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Kurosaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.07,0:16:44.01,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I see, so that's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.85,0:16:47.99,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Come out!\NI know you're here, Urahara!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.99,0:16:49.39,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,– What?!\N– What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.39,0:16:52.46,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,This is all your doing!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.36,0:17:02.23,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it seems you've figured it out…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.56,0:17:05.20,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,When did you notice?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.97,0:17:09.17,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,When I saw your hat\Non the ground just now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.56,0:17:13.80,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,See, Lirin? I told you,\Nyou were over acting!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.80,0:17:16.28,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You're sharper than I thought!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.81,0:17:23.12,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it,\Nyou had many chances to finish us off.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.68,0:17:25.16,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But you never did.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.16,0:17:28.06,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You just pushed us\Ninto tight situations.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.06,0:17:29.61,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That's what was strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.32,0:17:32.60,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Chad wasn't even harmed, was he?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.86,0:17:36.07,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! We even played Shogi\Nwith each other!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.34,0:17:38.10,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I never won once…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.82,0:17:41.54,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,So why did you do this?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.85,0:17:45.24,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Before that, can you return my hat?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.98,0:17:50.71,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Games can cultivate various senses.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.55,0:17:55.52,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Stamina, of course, intellect, team work,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.84,0:17:58.42,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,the ability to cope in\Nan instant, judgment…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.04,0:18:02.33,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It even strengthens\Nyour bonds to your friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.00,0:18:04.65,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,And most of all,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.65,0:18:07.70,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,it is a good chance to take\Na look at yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.04,0:18:09.90,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Look at myself?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.25,0:18:11.22,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.42,0:18:15.24,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Your Bankai…\Nyou can't use it, can you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.70,0:18:18.28,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What?! Is that true?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.28,0:18:19.34,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.31,0:18:24.21,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You are a Soul Reaper substitute.\NNot a Soul Reaper.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.85,0:18:28.46,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You may have been able to use it\Nquite a bit in the Soul Society, but…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.11,0:18:32.09,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Things aren't quite so easy\Nonce you've come back here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.90,0:18:35.84,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You especially shouldn't be\Nnaïve enough
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.84,0:18:38.68,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,to think that if things get tough,\Nyou have your Bankai.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.65,0:18:43.26,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's no wonder you can't use it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.75,0:18:47.18,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That aside…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.18,0:18:50.25,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Did you know that Yoruichi and\Nthe others are investigating something?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.24,0:18:54.32,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,She was rushing around at noon…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.32,0:18:56.33,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know the details,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.33,0:18:58.99,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,but there seems to be\Na bad phenomenon happening.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.99,0:19:00.71,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,A bad phenomenon?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.05,0:19:04.88,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yes… The Soul Society temporarily\Nclosed off passage
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.88,0:19:07.69,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,to the World of the Living to begin\Ninvestigating the specifics.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.02,0:19:08.99,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.99,0:19:11.84,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,that it has something to do\Nwith the Aizen incident?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.84,0:19:15.02,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,No. He only took away the Hogyoku.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.02,0:19:17.52,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He still needs a little more\Nthan a year to mature it
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.52,0:19:19.77,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,in order to demonstrate\Nits true power.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.28,0:19:23.02,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He probably won't make\Na move right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.51,0:19:26.61,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But in your current state…\Nyou're too weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.59,0:19:28.67,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Kurosaki…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.48,0:19:30.38,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.15,0:19:36.09,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I can't leave the troublesome issue\Nof the Hogyoku alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.79,0:19:40.62,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Please learn how to use\Nyour Bankai once more.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.62,0:19:42.62,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Please help me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.52,0:19:47.51,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.78,0:19:49.45,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,All ri--
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.45,0:19:51.61,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Really?! Oh, thank goodness!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.61,0:19:52.13,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hey…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.44,0:19:55.10,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What a heartless prostration…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.52,0:20:01.32,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,So, Kurosaki, let's cultivate\Nyour situation analysis and judgment skills.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.32,0:20:02.89,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Oh…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.89,0:20:06.54,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You allow your opponents to\Ntake advantage of you too often.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.54,0:20:08.14,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Do you use your head?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.36,0:20:10.80,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,In the end,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.80,0:20:17.25,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ishida, who's lost all his powers,\Nis better at doing that…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.26,0:20:20.22,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you, Ishida…?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.15,0:20:28.87,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I lost my Quincy powers\Nin the Soul Society…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.00,0:20:31.64,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Why didn't you tell us?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.64,0:20:34.81,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't use them because\Nyou couldn't use them?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.81,0:20:36.39,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Is that true, Ishida?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.95,0:20:38.64,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You sure are an idiot…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.04,0:20:40.32,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What did you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.32,0:20:42.70,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You're just endangering us.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.70,0:20:43.35,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh--?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.02,0:20:47.32,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not saying that it's dangerous\Nbecause you have no powers…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.67,0:20:51.45,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Fighting as a team means that\Nwe all can use various powers.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.92,0:20:55.09,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Your powers helped out this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.09,0:20:58.76,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You don't know if\Nyou'll be of any help unless you try!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.96,0:21:03.67,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But if you don't trust your friends,\Nyou can't fight…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.33,0:21:05.27,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.48,0:21:07.72,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Kurosaki…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.23,0:21:13.00,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,All right! Then let's go up\Nand have something to eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.68,0:21:16.97,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Tessai should have made\Nsomething delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.97,0:21:20.21,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what are you going to do\Nabout the destroyed town?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.94,0:21:25.69,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way we'd do that!\NThat was a hallucination as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.52,0:21:29.13,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Then where's everyone from class?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.13,0:21:31.16,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Right about now, they're…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.66,0:21:33.63,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hm--? Oh…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.05,0:21:35.52,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Where am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.52,0:21:37.08,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.08,0:21:38.36,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Where are we?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.36,0:21:41.26,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ah… You're all finally awake!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.26,0:21:44.56,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Ochi!\NWhy are we in the mountains?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.56,0:21:46.00,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Who knows…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.00,0:21:48.75,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But the stars are beautiful,\Nso it's all right!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.75,0:21:49.54,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.11,0:21:54.48,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Look! Wow… that's amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.48,0:21:56.41,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,– Is this okay?!\N– Is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.41,0:21:57.50,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I guess it is…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.40,0:21:59.79,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hey…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.79,0:22:00.51,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Kisuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.51,0:22:02.16,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,– Yes?\N– Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.56,0:22:09.36,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yoruichi?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.06,0:22:12.67,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I have something I want to tell to you all.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.73,0:22:14.79,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.39,0:22:18.94,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,A Bount has appeared!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.21,0:22:24.85,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Count one! And move on
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.85,0:22:27.54,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Count two! And take a break
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.54,0:22:30.04,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Count three! And think through
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.04,0:22:32.94,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll just go at my own pace
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.30,0:22:40.14,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Time goes by, and I get left behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.14,0:22:42.30,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But I say,\N“don’t forget that anxious feeling”
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.63,0:22:45.21,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,They tell me,\N“A reckless challenge is meaningless”
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.21,0:22:47.74,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But I say “don’t give up.”
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.74,0:22:57.38,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,(Offense!) At times when\Nthe going gets tough, I raise my voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.83,0:23:07.30,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,(Offense!) And head toward\Nthe direction of my goal.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.30,0:23:17.17,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,There is nothing to be afraid of\Nthat towering wall.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.46,0:23:27.11,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Never losing sight in this life\Nwithout answers
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.50,0:23:30.31,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Keep My Pace
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.22,0:23:40.56,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Count one! And move on
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.56,0:23:43.33,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Count two! And take a break
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.33,0:23:45.76,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Count three! And think through
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.76,0:23:50.23,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll just go at my own pace
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.92,0:23:54.84,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean,\Na new-type mod soul?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.84,0:23:57.20,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,They've got all sorts of bizarre powers.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.20,0:24:00.41,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Well, there's no way\Nthey can match my popularity.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.41,0:24:02.68,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I wonder about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.68,0:24:04.78,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Something terrible is going to happen\Nin the next episode.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.78,0:24:06.76,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What? Kon is going to disappear?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.76,0:24:07.61,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.61,0:24:18.62,OS,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The Golden Illustrated Guide\Nto Soul Reapers after these messages!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.96,0:24:21.41,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,– Illustrated Guide to Soul Reapers!\N– Golden!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.41,0:24:24.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Clothes really are uncomfortable…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.63,0:24:28.10,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?! Soi Fon! You're still here?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.69,0:24:30.65,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I told you to go home!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.65,0:24:34.88,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Oh…no… I've come all this way\Nto the World of the Living, so…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.88,0:24:35.74,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.10,0:24:40.79,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Um, Lady Yoruichi, today is… um…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.28,0:24:42.94,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.32,0:24:44.55,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Chocolate, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.65,0:24:56.66,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Tune in again!